sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User<br/>(kubectl/API)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as kueue-webhook-service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>mTLS
    participant Controller as kueue-controller-manager<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Scheduler as Kueue Scheduler<br/>(in-process)
    participant Cache as In-Memory Cache<br/>(in-process)
    participant ClusterAutoscaler as Cluster Autoscaler<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,ClusterAutoscaler: Flow 1: Job Submission and Admission

    User->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/batch/v1/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (User)<br/>Job: suspend=false
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-batch-v1-job<br/>mTLS (API Server client cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutate: suspend=true, labels
    K8sAPI-->>User: Job created (suspended)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Jobs, Workloads<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Job created event

    Controller->>Controller: Create Workload CR
    Controller->>K8sAPI: POST Workload CR<br/>Bearer Token (SA)

    Controller->>Scheduler: Evaluate admission
    Scheduler->>Cache: Check ClusterQueue quota
    Cache-->>Scheduler: Available quota

    alt Quota available
        Scheduler->>Controller: Admit workload
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH Job: suspend=false<br/>Add node selectors, tolerations
        K8sAPI-->>User: Job starts (Pods created)
    else Quota exhausted
        Scheduler->>Controller: Queue workload
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ProvisioningRequest<br/>Request node scaling
        K8sAPI->>ClusterAutoscaler: Watch ProvisioningRequest
        ClusterAutoscaler->>ClusterAutoscaler: Provision nodes
        ClusterAutoscaler->>K8sAPI: Update ProvisioningRequest status
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: ProvisioningRequest ready
        Controller->>Scheduler: Re-evaluate admission
        Scheduler->>Controller: Admit workload
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH Job: suspend=false
    end

    Note over User,ClusterAutoscaler: Flow 2: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>MetricsSvc: GET /metrics<br/>Bearer Token (SA)<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP TLS1.2+
    MetricsSvc-->>Prometheus: kueue_pending_workloads<br/>kueue_admitted_workloads_total<br/>kueue_cluster_queue_resource_usage

    Note over User,ClusterAutoscaler: Flow 3: Visibility API Query

    User->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/visibility.kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/<br/>clusterqueues/team-queue/pendingworkloads<br/>Bearer Token (User)
    K8sAPI->>VisibilityAPI: Forward request (in-process)
    VisibilityAPI->>Cache: Query pending workloads
    Cache-->>VisibilityAPI: Workload list
    VisibilityAPI-->>K8sAPI: JSON response
    K8sAPI-->>User: Pending workloads

    Note over User,ClusterAutoscaler: Flow 4: Multi-Cluster Dispatching (MultiKueue)

    Controller->>RemoteK8s: POST /apis/batch/v1/jobs<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS1.2+<br/>Kubeconfig credentials
    RemoteK8s-->>Controller: Job created on remote cluster
    Controller->>RemoteK8s: Watch job status<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    RemoteK8s-->>Controller: Job completed
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update local Workload status
